Title: Back to you
DateModified: '2019-03-03'
DatePublished: '2019-03-03'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/back-to-you
SetInCountry: India
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Victoria Gill
AuthorCountry: India
Text: Story of a teen indian searching the meaning of her existence,comes across a
  cheerful fun loving boy in Portugal while traveling.Twist is the boy is in his last
  stage of cancer but still lives to his fullest ,while the girl doesn't find life
  much intresting ,but when he enters her life , something unexpected happens in both
  the  lives.....join their beautiful journey to find a new level of love.
